            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_590gc' title='Col. 590GC &mdash; HL Deb 06 April 2004 vol 659 c590GC' name='column_590gc' href='#column_590gc' rel='bookmark'>590GC</a>
            belong to the Government; it would belong to the IOC. However, I am sure that a way can be found around that.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0659P0-09130'>
        <a name='S5LV0659P0_20040406_GCR_99'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-dominic-hubbard' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
