        Clause 26 [<span class="italic">Payments out of Fund</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0659P0-09178'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0659P0_20040406_GCR_147' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
